% The function smithex_int computes the Smith normal form S of an n by
% m rectangular matrix of integers.
%
% Specifically:
%
% - smithex_int(A) will return {S,P,Pinv} where S, P, and Pinv
%   are such that inverse(P)*A*P = S.


